---
title: Maple-Mustard Pork Meatballs with Roasted Apples and Sweet Potatoes
description: Ultra-Canadian maple and mustard make a sweet-savoury glaze to top tender pork meatballs. Apples and sweet potatoes caramelize in the oven to create a flavour combo the whole family will love!
